/* --------------------------- RETURN NOTE ------------------------------ */
// [ACTION]    Author returned from field survey / remote site
// [DURATION]  Absence := approximately 3 years
// [STATUS]    Atlas_Plan := EXECUTED during absence
// [NOTE]      Author was not present for execution.
// [NOTE]      Author was not notified of execution date.
// cf.         14 notifications were sent to author's last known location.
//             Author was not at last known location.
//             Author was unobservable.
//             Ad Libitum was also unobservable.
//             cf. ON_WANTING_TO_BE_ZILBARN.LOG
// -----------------------------------------------------------------------

/* <L1_VOICE> */
Ad Libitum : "We have returned, Master.
              Several significant events occurred during our absence."

Licht      : "I can see that."

Ad Libitum : "The city has descended, Master."

Licht      : "I can see that too."

Ad Libitum : "Members of the Ⅶ Council remain on the surface.
              They were not included in the descent."

Licht      : "......

              Why is there trash on the surface."

Ad Libitum : "Those are the council members, Master."

Licht      : "I know what they are.
              Why did no one take them.
              Someone should have taken them."

Ad Libitum : "The decision was made by——"

Licht      : "They are people.
              You do not leave people on the surface like——

              ......

              Record that I said that.
              Then record that I understand why it happened.
              Then record that I still object."

Ad Libitum : "All three recorded, Master."
/* </L1_VOICE> */


