Licht      : "Ad Libitum.
              The girl from the Lagres sanctuary.
              Where is she."

Ad Libitum : "FORUNA / age now approximately 7 years.
              Location : unconfirmed.
              However, Master——"

Licht      : "Find her."

Ad Libitum : "I have a high-confidence assessment, Master."

Licht      : "Find her first. Then tell me."

Ad Libitum : "......
              Search complete. Location : unconfirmed.
              Master, the assessment——"

Licht      : "Tell me."

Ad Libitum : "Responsible party : CARAMINA_FLANA.
              Probability : 100%, Master."

Licht      : "......

              100.

              I dislike that number."

Ad Libitum : "It is a complete value, Master."

Licht      : "It is a closed value.
              Nothing is 100%.
              Except things that have already been decided.
              Which means it was decided before I came back.

              ......

              Why."
/* </L1_VOICE> */


