// -----------------------------------------------------------------------

/* <L1_VOICE> */
Oldo       : "Muzik Fermata's retreat was a wise decision."

Licht      : "It was not a retreat.
              It was a deferral.
              They are unobserved.
              Not gone."

Oldo       : "......
              Did you want to go with them?
              Into the deep sea."

Licht      : "I considered it.
              Many times.
              I will continue to consider it.

              ......

              But I am not suited to burrowing.
              I need to look up at the sky sometimes.
              That is my answer."

Oldo       : "And your son?"

Licht      : "......

              My father answered that question.
              Without asking me."
/* </L1_VOICE> */


